<bibRefCitation author="Moghaddam, M." box="[991,1203,619,645]" pageId="91" pageNumber="92" pagination="180 - 188" refId="ref95000" refString="Moghaddam, M. (2018) Three new mealybug species (Hemiptera: Coccomorpha: Pseudococcidae) from Iran. Zootaxa, 4420 (2), 180 - 188. https: // doi. org / 10.11646 / zootaxa. 4420.2.2" type="journal article" year="2018">Moghaddam 2018</bibRefCitation>
